Class ThreeDimensionalShapes

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shapes
      • ThreeDimensionalShapes
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AngleBase3DShapes, NoAngleBase3DShapes

    public class ThreeDimensionalShapes
extends Shapes
    Version:
    1.0

    This is a subclass of the Shapes class that will hold only #D shapes, In the shapes class we can determine that all 3D shape must have a volume and surface area.

    Author:
    Alex Wong wong4a@gmail.com
